data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2022-built, modern home in the coveted Evergreen community. This residence is a testament to luxury and functionality, offering an all-concrete block construction that ensures durability and longevity. Step inside and discover a thoughtfully designed one-story layout that optimizes living space with a seamless open concept. The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen strategically positioned between the inviting living area and the elegant dining room. Boasting high-end finishes, the kitchen features granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and a complete suite of appliances, including a refrigerator, built-in dishwasher, electric range, and microwave. Retreat to your private owner's suite, strategically placed at the rear of the home for maximum tranquility. The ensuite bathroom is a spa-like oasis, perfect for relaxation and rejuvenation. Two additional bedrooms share a well-appointed second bathroom, providing comfortable accommodations for family or guests. Built in 2022, everything in this home is just a year old, ensuring you enjoy modern amenities and energy efficiency. The covered lanai is ideal for outdoor gatherings. This property boasts an unbeatable location, with access to the Evergreen community pool and cabana. With an incredibly low HOA fee under $150/month, this home is also zoned in an excellent school district. It offers quick access to Anna Maria Island, Bradenton Beach, Siesta Key Beach, UTC Mall, Lakewood Ranch, fine dining, shopping, and IMG Academy. Take advantage of the opportunity to make this East Bradenton gem your new home!
